      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"4. BRONELLY TIMMY was a last start winner (24.26) at this track in a T3 RSTW and will jump from box 4 for the first time. All two career wins have been here at this trip. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to be right there at the finish again. 8. WHERE'S HUNTLY is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 1.2 lengths at Warrnambool in a handy 22.57 beating Black Hawk. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in three starts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. 6. RAE'S RAINBOW looks close to another win after finishing third last time (24.59) in a T3 RSTW at this track. Comes out of a solid form race last start. Will give a great sight again. 7. BLUE TROMBONE has top-three claims while fresh from a six-and-a-half weeks break.\",\"runners\":[4,8,6,7],\"exclusive\":false}",
